{"tid":1215053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暴徒最新交通癱瘓計劃整合","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T07:59:31.000Z","uid":86509,"like":126,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb2925be60cecdfe5632ad1fb123731431a2ab1","tid":1215053,"uid":86509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:58:18.000Z","msg":"佢哋想每日<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">返工時間或假日最多人流時候</span></span>全面阻塞交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先係不斷撘地鐵各個中轉站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">九龍塘 大圍 紅磡<br />\n調景嶺 油塘 鰂魚涌 北角<br />\n金鐘 中環<br />\n太子 旺角 油麻地</span><br />\n<br />\n（即其他時間唔會阻塞，假日會改係人流最多時段做）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞到佢哋不停開閂門<br />\n1.最後一秒衝上車<br />\n2.死都要逼上車<br />\n3.唔覺意係咁夾到個袋<br />\n4.唔覺意用長遮、篋或bb車啲轆等物件卡住條罅<br />\n5.唔覺意跌嘢落東鐵路軌或罅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人唔舒服 鬧交 打架 有嘢卡住條罅<br />\n㩒緊急聯絡掣搵職員幫手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VgEhexe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgEhexe.png&h=8617fc09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有搵車或食油或故意漏油去塞住呢啲主要道路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋會扮晒唔小心去做呢啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全面交通癱瘓<br />\n而完全合法<br />\n又無組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要扮到好認真返工返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警察都吹班人唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我錯啦唔應該支持政府<br />\n求下你哋停手啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>另外若宣佈二讀正式開始，就會立即停止玩車，一個鐘時間內飛奔去金鐘站</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"aa1604d8f8e05eb88f579900385d4147bfda2900","tid":1215053,"uid":108016,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"星期六日唔好拖篋坐東鐵<br />\n會搞到啲遊客<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406c064fe3948627c9fbbfee489626e45579f3cd","tid":1215053,"uid":86509,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHPEtk5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHPEtk5.png&h=e0650ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zs39Qzu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZs39Qzu.png&h=3d5a172e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNetmF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNetmF8.png&h=6a8ffb00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P0qwjsM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP0qwjsM.png&h=ddd4ac0a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90M7Cew.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90M7Cew.png&h=40abe25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBp5oUx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBp5oUx.png&h=7917b9f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1PMSNN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1PMSNN.png&h=d9ef5a4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f92ee33605835d8acf802333eee8891a2f5109df","tid":1215053,"uid":229017,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"暴乜撚嘢徒"},{"pid":"2512426df7b444ceb68f59d0f9e90b989c7e865a","tid":1215053,"uid":86509,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f92ee33